&lt;p&gt;We are looking for one or two motivated and reliable full time GP Partner(s) to join our surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a small, friendly practice in a village setting, approximately 15 minutes from Junction 32 off the M4.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have a supportive administration team to help assist with the working operations of the surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;High QOF/QAIF achievers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our computer system is INPS Vision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;List size approx. 5,500.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in joining us please can you contact Dr A O Afelumo on abimbola.afelumo@wales.nhs.uk or speak to the Practice Manager on 01443 450340 Practice Manager at kate.mills@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
